{"id":773,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":773,"title":"Jeremiah 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Israel and Judah are called to repentance—Jeremiah laments for the miseries of Judah."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.1","order":"02.25.004.50902"},["b","1"],"If thou wilt return, O Israel, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", return unto me: and if thou wilt put away thine abominations out of my sight, then shalt thou not remove."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.2","order":"02.25.004.50903"},["b","2"],"And thou shalt swear, The",["span.smallCaps",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Lord"]],"liveth, in truth, in judgment, and in righteousness; and the nations shall bless themselves in him, and in him shall they glory."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.3","order":"02.25.004.50904"},["b","3"],"¶For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"to the men of Judah and Jerusalem,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Break"],"up your fallow ground, and sow not among",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"thorns"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.4","order":"02.25.004.50905"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Circumcise"],"yourselves to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and take away the foreskins of your heart, ye men of Judah and inhabitants of Jerusalem: lest my fury come forth like fire, and burn that none can quench",["i","it,"],"because of the evil of your doings."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.5","order":"02.25.004.50906"},["b","5"],"Declare ye in Judah, and publish in Jerusalem; and say, Blow ye the trumpet in the land: cry, gather together, and say, Assemble yourselves, and let us go into the defenced cities."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.6","order":"02.25.004.50907"},["b","6"],"Set up the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"standard"],"toward",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"Zion"],": retire, stay not: for I will bring evil from the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"north"],", and a great destruction."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.7","order":"02.25.004.50908"},["b","7"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"lion"],"is come up from his thicket, and the destroyer of the Gentiles is on his way; he is gone forth from his place to make thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"land"],"desolate;",["i","and"],"thy cities shall be laid waste, without an inhabitant."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.8","order":"02.25.004.50909"},["b","8"],"For this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"gird"],"you with sackcloth, lament and howl: for the fierce",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"anger"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"is not turned back from us."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.9","order":"02.25.004.50910"},["b","9"],"And it shall come to pass at that day, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","that"],"the heart of the king shall perish, and the heart of the princes; and the priests shall be astonished, and the prophets shall wonder."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.10","order":"02.25.004.50911"},["b","10"],"Then said I, Ah, Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"! surely thou hast greatly deceived this people and Jerusalem, saying, Ye shall have peace; whereas the sword reacheth unto the soul."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.11","order":"02.25.004.50912"},["b","11"],"At that time shall it be said to this people and to Jerusalem, A dry",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"wind"],"of the high places in the wilderness toward the daughter of my people, not to fan, nor to cleanse,"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.12","order":"02.25.004.50913"},["b","12"],["i","Even"],"a full wind from those",["i","places"],"shall come unto me: now also will I give sentence against them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.13","order":"02.25.004.50914"},["b","13"],"Behold, he shall come up as",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"clouds"],", and his chariots",["i","shall be"],"as a whirlwind: his horses are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"swifter"],"than eagles. Woe unto us! for we are spoiled."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.14","order":"02.25.004.50915"},["b","14"],"O Jerusalem,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"wash"],"thine heart from wickedness, that thou mayest be saved. How long shall thy vain thoughts lodge within thee?"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.15","order":"02.25.004.50916"},["b","15"],"For a voice declareth from Dan, and publisheth affliction from mount Ephraim."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.16","order":"02.25.004.50917"},["b","16"],"Make ye mention to the nations; behold, publish against Jerusalem,",["i","that"],"watchers come from a far country, and give out their voice against the cities of Judah."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.17","order":"02.25.004.50918"},["b","17"],"As keepers of a field, are they against her round about; because she hath been rebellious against me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.18","order":"02.25.004.50919"},["b","18"],"Thy way and thy doings have procured these",["i","things"],"unto thee; this",["i","is"],"thy wickedness, because it is bitter, because it reacheth unto thine heart."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.19","order":"02.25.004.50920"},["b","19"],"¶My",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"bowels"],", my bowels! I am",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"pained"],"at my very heart; my heart maketh a noise in me; I cannot hold my peace, because thou hast heard, O my soul, the sound of the trumpet, the alarm of war."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.20","order":"02.25.004.50921"},["b","20"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Destruction"],"upon destruction is cried; for the whole land is spoiled: suddenly are my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"tents"],"spoiled,",["i","and"],"my curtains in a moment."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.21","order":"02.25.004.50922"},["b","21"],"How long shall I see the standard,",["i","and"],"hear the sound of the trumpet?"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.22","order":"02.25.004.50923"},["b","22"],"For my people",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"foolish"],", they have not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"known"],"me; they",["i","are"],"sottish children, and they have none understanding: they",["i","are"],"wise to do",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"evil"],", but to do good they have no knowledge."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.23","order":"02.25.004.50924"},["b","23"],"I beheld the earth, and, lo,",["i","it was"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"without form"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"void"],"; and the heavens, and they",["i","had"],"no light."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.24","order":"02.25.004.50925"},["b","24"],"I beheld the mountains, and, lo, they trembled, and all the hills moved lightly."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.25","order":"02.25.004.50926"},["b","25"],"I beheld, and, lo,",["i","there was"],"no man, and all the birds of the heavens were fled."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.26","order":"02.25.004.50927"},["b","26"],"I beheld, and, lo, the fruitful place",["i","was"],"a wilderness, and all the cities thereof were broken down at the presence of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","and"],"by his fierce anger."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.27","order":"02.25.004.50928"},["b","27"],"For thus hath the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said, The whole land shall be desolate; yet will I not make a full",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"end"],"."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.28","order":"02.25.004.50929"},["b","28"],"For this shall the earth mourn, and the heavens above be black: because I have spoken",["i","it,"],"I have purposed",["i","it,"],"and will not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"repent"],", neither will I turn back from it."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.29","order":"02.25.004.50930"},["b","29"],"The whole city shall flee for the noise of the horsemen and bowmen; they shall go into thickets, and climb up upon the rocks: every city",["i","shall be"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"forsaken"],", and not a man dwell therein."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.30","order":"02.25.004.50931"},["b","30"],"And",["i","when"],"thou",["i","art"],"spoiled, what wilt thou do? Though thou clothest thyself with crimson, though thou deckest thee with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"ornaments"],"of gold, though thou",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"rentest thy face"],"with painting, in vain shalt thou make thyself fair;",["i","thy"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_30c"},"lovers"],"will despise thee, they will seek thy life."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.31","order":"02.25.004.50932"},["b","31"],"For I have heard a voice as of a woman in travail,",["i","and"],"the anguish as of her that bringeth forth her first child, the voice of the daughter of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"Zion"],",",["i","that"],"bewaileth herself,",["i","that"],"spreadeth her hands,",["i","saying,"],"Woe",["i","is"],"me now! for my soul is wearied because of murderers."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.2a","order":"02.25.004.50933"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/16.14"},"Jer. 16:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.3a","order":"02.25.004.50935"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.12"},"Hosea 10:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.3b","order":"02.25.004.50937"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.7"},"Matt. 13:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.4a","order":"02.25.004.50939"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/circumcision"},"TG Circumcision"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.6a","order":"02.25.004.50941"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ensign"},"TG Ensign"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.6b","order":"02.25.004.50943"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.6c","order":"02.25.004.50945"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/1.14.13-14"},"Jer. 1:14 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/6.1"},"6:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.22"},"10:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.7a","order":"02.25.004.50947"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.19"},"Jer. 49:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.7b","order":"02.25.004.50949"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-land-of"},"TG Israel, Land of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.8a","order":"02.25.004.50951"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.13.1-13"},"Joel 1:13 (1–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.8b","order":"02.25.004.50953"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.12.12,17,21"},"Isa. 9:12 (12, 17, 21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.11a","order":"02.25.004.50955"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/51.1.1-2"},"Jer. 51:1 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.13a","order":"02.25.004.50957"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.9"},"Ezek. 38:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.13b","order":"02.25.004.50959"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.19"},"Lam. 4:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.14a","order":"02.25.004.50961"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cleanliness"},"TG Cleanliness"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purification"},"Purification"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purity"},"Purity"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.19a","order":"02.25.004.50963"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.20"},"Lam. 1:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.19b","order":"02.25.004.50965"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pain"},"TG Pain"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.20a","order":"02.25.004.50967"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.26"},"Ezek. 7:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.20b","order":"02.25.004.50969"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/10.20"},"Jer. 10:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.22a","order":"02.25.004.50971"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/foolishness"},"TG Foolishness"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.22b","order":"02.25.004.50973"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/5.13"},"Mosiah 5:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.22c","order":"02.25.004.50975"},["b","22c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.4.1-7"},"Hel. 12:4 (1–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.23a","order":"02.25.004.50977"},["b","23a"],["span.small","OR"],"empty and desolate."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.23b","order":"02.25.004.50979"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.2.2-26"},"Moses 2:2 (2–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.27a","order":"02.25.004.50981"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.10"},"Jer. 5:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.28a","order":"02.25.004.50983"},["b","28a"],["span.small","HEB"],"relent."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.29a","order":"02.25.004.50985"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.30a","order":"02.25.004.50987"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.13"},"Hosea 2:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"30b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.30b","order":"02.25.004.50989"},["b","30b"],["span.small","OR"],"enlargest thine eyes."],["div",{"id":"30c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.30c","order":"02.25.004.50991"},["b","30c"],["span.small","HEB"],"sensuous lovers."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.31a","order":"02.25.004.50993"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.17"},"Lam. 1:17"],"."]]}
